PLAUDITS: Tova Borgnine, Sybil Brand and Ginny Mancini receive halos at the 
Women in Show Business luncheon today at the Beverly Hills Hotel. . . . The 
Beverly and Sidney Kline Garden will be dedicated today at the City of Hope. 
