<P>
As a taxpaying individual, I was very cool to the idea of a taxpayer takeover 
of San Diego Gas &amp; Electric. Now that SDG&amp;E is trying to prevent us 
from finding out the facts related to this issue, I can see I was wrong. 
</P>
<P>
They, obviously, have something to hide or they wouldn't prevent the Water 
Authority from spending a relatively small amount of money. 
</P>
<P>
Bad move, SDG&amp;E, you lost my vote. 
</P>
