SPORTS FRANCHISES; LANDRY, TOM; JONES, JERRY; JOHNSON, JIMMY; COACHES; DALLAS 
COWBOYS; SCHRAMM, TEX; ACQUISITIONS; BRIGHT, H R (BUM); TEAM OWNERS 
</P>
</SUBJECT>
