Some Recent British Acquisitions in Orange County 
</P>
<P>
General Automation Corp., Anaheim, this year received $4.1 million in financing 
from Sanderson PLC that can be converted into a 51% stake in General 
Automation. 
</P>
<P>
EECO Inc.'s video text division, acquired this year by Paltex Editing &amp; 
Production Systems Ltd. for $375,000 cash and a long-term note for an 
undisclosed amount. 
</P>
<P>
A 50% stake in Campbell Automotive Group, Irvine, acquired in 1988 by Lex 
Service PLC for $13.5 million. 
</P>
<P>
